@ssbarnea the issue showed up again, this time it was related to delegation. I could solve it by remounting the cgroup fs like this:
`mount -o remount,nsdelegate /sys/fs/cgroup`
I think it's persistent and I don't know how to configure it in advance (at least on Debian).
